      "creatureType": "",
      "blurb": "Human thug",
      "publicNotes": "<h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p><strong>Role:</strong> one of Devargo's dozen hired muscle — washed-out soldiers and sailors kept sober by fear of the King of Spiders. They prefer <strong>saps</strong>: troublemakers are knocked out, not killed, then fed to Chittersnap below.</p><p><strong>Tactics &amp; morale:</strong> 4 work the pier (C1), 6 the deck (C2). They fight until reduced to a sliver of HP, then flee. Once Devargo raises the alarm, more arrive at one per round. Bluff/Diplomacy gets past them far more cheaply than a fight.</p>",
